{"tid":2114963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華企同方威視獲加國安檢合約  恐資料送中 加外長稱會重新審視","createTime":"2020-07-19T07:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T08:05:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e89a5fa4e30af139a82cfb9fd7aa2f0c8c78e3c","tid":2114963,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200719/23YGTGIATXRFTQKBKJ4UAH3BEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200719%2F23YGTGIATXRFTQKBKJ4UAH3BEU%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=d85c93f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200719%2F23YGTGIATXRFTQKBKJ4UAH3BEU%2F&h=647a4ff9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200719/23YGTGIATXRFTQKBKJ4UAH3BEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華企同方威視獲加國安檢合約 <br />\n恐資料送中 加外長稱會重新審視<br />\n<br />\n加拿大與中國關係因孟晚舟案及康明凱案跌入冰點，但加國政府竟爆出欲與中國企業同方威視（Nuctech）簽訂一份680萬加元（約3,885萬港元）合同，為旗下全球170個大使館、領事館及高級專員提供X光安檢機等設備。同方威視的創辦人正是前國家主席胡錦濤之子胡海峰，消息震驚加國，認為做法難以理解。加拿大外交部長商鵬飛昨急澄清政府未購入同方威視設備，已指示官員審視指標方法。<br />\n<br />\n同方威視由胡錦濤之子胡海峰於1997年創立，屬於中國清華大學的分支機構之一，胡擔任該公司總裁至2008年。胡離開全力踏入政壇，現正擔任浙江省麗水市市委書記。同方近。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FjRrDHLDzymy06JhN_asIK_1cr0=/640x442/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TALD7DKCGAASNMRLAGECGOXMVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFjRrDHLDzymy06JhN_asIK_1cr0%3D%2F640x442%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTALD7DKCGAASNMRLAGECGOXMVE.jpg&h=93fcfbc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同方威視取得加拿大定單，製作X光安檢設備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LAW4-riCCZArwZVuF3Z0M2FYljo=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PLGSPG5AYTB47WQT4IQTMWLTVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLAW4-riCCZArwZVuF3Z0M2FYljo%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPLGSPG5AYTB47WQT4IQTMWLTVI.jpg&h=a8f62df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡海峰曾長時間擔任同方威視的總裁。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zGkIq9vUxTkF3JRAb3qd2KAST_M=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DMT2E4U3LNR63TF2SZLS3PDI4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzGkIq9vUxTkF3JRAb3qd2KAST_M%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDMT2E4U3LNR63TF2SZLS3PDI4E.jpg&h=82ad4889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工作人員正測試一套行李安檢設備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為使館提供X光機<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：曾涉3.8億巨額賄賂案<br />\n<br />\n歐美各國似乎正密謀對付同方威視之際，加拿大《國家郵報》（National Post）在當地時間周二（14日）報道，同方威視贏得一紙重大標書。加拿大政府出資680萬加元，由同方威視負責協助加拿大全球各大使館、領事館、高級。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事件在當地引起爭議，前加拿大駐北京大使趙樸(Guy Saint-Jacques)希望加拿大收回招標結果，原因是價低者得會造成漏洞，指中國協助國企贏得國際合約，不惜資助40%，他。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n商鵬飛回應指，目前仍未向同方威視購買任何設備，並表示目前已經指示官員去審查採購安全設備時招標方法，並表示會採取一。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hJf6EybcPxUOeIaLPIsmfMlf_Yw=/687x572/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HYHO26NHYIEQUAET6KVWBP7I4U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhJf6EybcPxUOeIaLPIsmfMlf_Yw%3D%2F687x572%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHYHO26NHYIEQUAET6KVWBP7I4U.gif&h=39c05386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華大使盼中加合作<br />\n<br />\n此外，中加關係在孟晚舟案後急劇轉差，中國駐加拿大大使叢培武近日參。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大《國家郵報》"},{"pid":"c2fb75223760b5a879d6e0b83492910cfcd4b0e7","tid":2114963,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNjnNbj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNjnNbj.png&h=3b49f155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明啦"}]}